loaded with antioxidants, potassium and lutein, amongst other goodness. You can buy the dried powder in health food stores or online. It is not crucial to the recipe, although it does lift the flavour with its lovely tartness. This slice is still delicious without it."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","2h 45m","24 pieces"]}